                'birthday' => '1974-12-27',
                'deceased' => NULL,
                'image' => 'Masi_Oka_1453899892.jpg',
            'bio' => 'Masi Oka was born on December 27, 1974 in Tokyo, Japan as Masayori Oka. He is known for his work on Hawaii Five-0 (2010), Heroes (2006) and Friends with Benefits (2011).',
