            'bio' => 'Bill Hader was born on June 7, 1978 in Tulsa, Oklahoma, USA. He is an actor and writer, known for Superbad (2007), Saturday Night Live (1975) and Inside Out (2015). He has been married to Maggie Carey since 2006. They have three children.',
