            'bio' => 'Hank Azaria was born on April 25, 1964 in Queens, New York City, New York, USA as Henry Albert Azaria. He is an actor, known for The Simpsons (1989), The Simpsons Movie (2007) and Godzilla (1998). He was previously married to Helen Hunt.',
