            'bio' => 'John Oliver was born on April 23, 1977 in Birmingham, England as John William Oliver. He is a writer and actor, known for The Daily Show (1996), John Oliver: Terrifying Times (2008) and The Rally to Restore Sanity and/or Fear (2010).',
