            'bio' => 'Greg Grunberg was born on July 11, 1966 in Los Angeles, California, USA as Gregory Phillip Grunberg. He is an actor and producer, known for Heroes (2006), Star Wars: Episode VII - The Force Awakens (2015) and Hollow Man (2000). He has been married to Elizabeth Dawn Wershow since December 19, 1992. They have three children.',
