            'bio' => 'Ahmed Best was born on August 19, 1973 in New York City, New York, USA. He is an actor and producer, known for Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace (1999), Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones (2002) and Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith (2005).',
