            'bio' => 'Jimmy Smits was born on July 9, 1955 in Brooklyn, New York City, New York, USA as Jimmy L. Smits. He is an actor and producer, known for Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith (2005), NYPD Blue (1993) and Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones (2002). He was previously married to Barbara Smits.',
