                'surname' => 'Morton',
                'birthday' => '1947-10-18',
                'deceased' => NULL,
                'image' => 'Joe_Morton_1453935413.jpg',
            'bio' => 'Joe Morton was born on October 18, 1947 in New York, New York, USA. He is a television, film, and theater actor, best known for The Brother from Another Planet (1984), Terminator 2: Judgment Day (1991), Eureka (2006), and Scandal (2014). He also writes and directs, and is a singer/songwriter.',
