            'bio' => 'Dean Norris was born on April 8, 1963 in South Bend, Indiana, USA as Dean Joseph Norris. He is an actor, known for Breaking Bad (2008), Little Miss Sunshine (2006) and Terminator 2: Judgment Day (1991). He has been married to Bridget since April 2001. They have five children.',
