            'bio' => 'Moon Bloodgood was born on September 20, 1975 in Alliance, Nebraska, USA as Korinna Moon Bloodgood. She is known for her work on Terminator Salvation (2009), Falling Skies (2011) and The Sessions (2012). She has been married to Grady Hall since August 2011. They have one child.',
