            'bio' => 'Julie White was born on June 4, 1961 in San Diego, California, USA as Julie Karen White. She is an actress, known for Transformers (2007), Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen (2009) and Transformers: Dark of the Moon (2011). She was previously married to Christopher Conner and Carl Pandel.',
