            'bio' => 'Kevin Durand was born on January 14, 1974 in Thunder Bay, Ontario, Canada as Kevin Serge Durand. He is an actor, known for X-Men Origins: Wolverine (2009), Real Steel (2011) and I Am Number Four (2011). He has been married to Sandra Cho since October 1, 2010.',
