                'image' => '_Aacute_lex_Gonz_aacute_lez_1453936620.jpg',
            'bio' => '&Aacute;lex Gonz&aacute;lez was born on August 13, 1980 in Madrid, Spain as Augusto Alejandro Jos&eacute; Gonz&aacute;lez. He is an actor, known for X-Men: First Class (2011), Scorpion in Love (2013) and El Pr&iacute;ncipe (2014).',
