                'deceased' => NULL,
                'image' => 'Tyler_Mane_1453936926.jpg',
            'bio' => 'Tyler Mane was born on December 8, 1966 in Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, Canada as Daryl Karolat. He is an actor and producer, known for X-Men (2000), Halloween (2007) and Troy (2004). He has been married to Renae Geerlings since September 3, 2007. He was previously married to Jean Goertz.',
