            'bio' => 'Terry O&#039;Quinn was born on July 15, 1952 in Sault Ste. Marie, Michigan, USA as Terrance Quinn. He is an actor, known for Lost (2004), Primal Fear (1996) and The X Files (1998). He was previously married to Lori O&#039;Quinn.',
